== 歷史 ==
此站在1915年6月22日啟用，是[[BMT第四大道線|BMT第四大道線]]前往[[59街車站_(BMT第四大道線)|59街]]的原初部分<ref name="Station Opening">{{cite web|title=Through Tube to Coney, 48 Minutes: First Train on Fourth Avenue Route Beats West End Line Eleven Minutes|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/57548404|via=[[Newspapers.com|Newspapers.com]]|publisher=[[Brooklyn_Daily_Eagle|Brooklyn Daily Eagle]]|accessdate=June 29, 2015|date=June 22, 1915|archive-date=2018-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108185202/http://www.newspapers.com/image/57548404/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2022年4月12日，一名头戴防毒面具的男子在站内[[2022年布鲁克林地铁袭击|投掷烟雾弹并开枪]]，造成26人受伤，双向列车服务暂停<ref>{{cite web |title=Police seeking ‘person of interest’ after Brooklyn subway shooting |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2022/04/12/brooklyn-subway-shooting/ |website=Washington Post |accessdate=2022-04-14 |date=2022-04-12 |archive-date=2022-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412140516/https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2022/04/12/brooklyn-subway-shooting/ }}</ref>。

